    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Beneath 是一款受洛夫克拉夫特式恐怖故事风格启发的生存类第一人称射击游戏，由一对热爱恐怖与射击游戏的兄弟创立的小型工作室打造。稀缺的弹药、凶残无情的敌人，还有充满未知的氛围，共同构成了这场长达 10 多小时并由剧情驱动的单人战役，既为资深玩家量身打造，也适合寻求高难度挑战的老派游戏爱好者 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>经验丰富的潜水员 Noah Quinn 在一次例行深海探险中意外陷入混乱，被困在深海之中，而那里潜藏着远古的邪恶力量。随着补给逐渐耗尽，噩梦般的怪物步步紧逼，Noah 必须直面恐怖的变异生物，揭开一场危及人类存亡的邪恶阴谋。   </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>女儿的生命危在旦夕，Noah 被逼至极限，与时间赛跑，在绝境中奋力求生。他能否揭开真相，阻止上古邪恶重现于世？抑或一切都将被深渊吞噬？</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/50e1e6836323a6e1581a53acc383fba7.poster.avif?t=1766081214\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/50e1e6836323a6e1581a53acc383fba7.webm?t=1766081214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/50e1e6836323a6e1581a53acc383fba7.mp4?t=1766081214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/ed0deb4d8e0dde20118be8a4f2042f93.avif?t=1766081214\" width=1560 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Beneath 由一对满怀热忱的兄弟打造，它的故事背景设定在北极深海之下，把洛夫克拉夫特式的恐怖与充满动作感的电影式叙事融合在一起。你必须与时间赛跑，寻找治疗女儿的办法，在各个研究站之间辗转求生，并逐步揭露 Omnium Corporation 背后的险恶阴谋。</strong>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/2fe85f5356fa424db4971c05049cb8cb.poster.avif?t=1766081214\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/2fe85f5356fa424db4971c05049cb8cb.webm?t=1766081214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/2fe85f5356fa424db4971c05049cb8cb.mp4?t=1766081214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/59a22629e7791dcb3474f17db68dc7b9.avif?t=1766081214\" width=1560 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>你会遇到种类繁多的恐怖敌人，其中既有冷酷无情的士兵也有丑陋畸形的洛夫克拉夫特式怪物。在弹药有限的情况下，你想要活下来就必须谨慎分配资源，升级武器装备，并且还要巧妙利用环境陷阱。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/d71228786e3892883c8a30b8bb4bafb7.poster.avif?t=1766081214\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/d71228786e3892883c8a30b8bb4bafb7.webm?t=1766081214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/d71228786e3892883c8a30b8bb4bafb7.mp4?t=1766081214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/1c50355d3a287aef10ef13a1bc1efec9.avif?t=1766081214\" width=1560 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>深渊中的噩梦已然苏醒。随着理智逐渐崩溃，你会更容易受到扭曲幻象与邪神怪物的身心攻击。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/f44a8eb6060583c0fb01f3925afbba47.poster.avif?t=1766081214\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/f44a8eb6060583c0fb01f3925afbba47.webm?t=1766081214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/f44a8eb6060583c0fb01f3925afbba47.mp4?t=1766081214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593230/extras/847bbab9e6e28c0f3ca6c67a2d0a786c.avif?t=1766081214\" width=1560 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回归经典：这款游戏由一对毕生热爱此类题材的兄弟创立的小型工作室倾力打造，而这部作品正是他们献给经典之作的一封情书。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为生存而战：极具攻击性的士兵们正对你展开疯狂追捕，而异界恐怖也在暗中潜行，时刻威胁着你的生命。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武装上阵：使用多种可升级武器，在时刻可能被摧毁的环境中近距离激烈交火，力求生存。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >理智受袭：在面对梦魇般的幻象和怪物时，你依然要努力保持头脑清醒。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深渊之秘：探索废弃研究站的遗迹，调查邮件、掌上电脑和幸存者的记录，逐步揭开一场深藏于海底的黑暗阴谋。 </p>",
